Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:14.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,同樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,聖誕節你送我的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:35.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你送我的圍巾也很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  和家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他們在和熟人聊天  看樣子要聊上很久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  我們家也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說  一起參拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:02:59.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,人還挺多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是元旦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖說很正常  但全是一家子或者情侶一起來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我倆啥也不是  總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個  我記得是二行禮二拍手一行禮對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好像沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望今年不被高木同學捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你許了什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望不被我捉弄之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哈哈  我猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡  已經被她捉弄上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學許了什麼願
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,保密  你猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正就是希望能捉弄我之類的唄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:11.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就算不許願也能捉弄到你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  來比今年第一場比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:30.62,Takagi san—Picture 10-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz271.2\move(978.667,453.333,1018.667,453.333,0,4824)}神籤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:30.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們比抽籤  運勢好的人贏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  誰能贏全憑運氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:38.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年伊始  我要改變被捉弄的運勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  我接受你的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看她這從容不迫的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:49.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要抽個好簽  一定要贏過你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來吧  大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吉還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好像僅次於大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,應該比中吉小吉要好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  只要高木同學抽不到大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就至少是平手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:19.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,請給我兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一共400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:36.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望身體健康？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說的是我許願的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡  大好新年竟然屢戰屢敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,無論如何我都要猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我媽媽打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我正在喝甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:06.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起  家人叫我了  我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  還想和我再待一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  也不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,, 我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年第一次比賽也贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,和你見面真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明年的抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一定會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你的意思是明年也要一起新年參拜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  要是能偶遇的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望明年也能和你一起新年參拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  明年也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正每年我爸媽都會和熟人聊上半天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒想到願望這麼快就實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:14.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我許的願望是希望西片再找我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說  你肯定說謊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
