Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,積雪了  積雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.28,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.472\move(1390,550,1448,548,0,2030)\fs50\t(0,2030,\fs55)}收到新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.28,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.472\move(1054,672,1064,684,0,2030)\fs50\t(0,2030,\fs55)}滑動顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好啊  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  西片  真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是因為積雪了所以興高采烈的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒啊  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:09.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過積雪確實很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:14.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  我記得已經五年沒有積這麼多雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃  我可沒有興高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.52,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.53\an1\fs40\pos(402,396)}要不要現在\N去空地比賽堆雪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.52,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.53\fs40\pos(688,490)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說趕緊開始吧  這個所謂的堆雪人比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是呢  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為會被雪弄濕  所以今天我戴了這雙手套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,厚手套嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,估計她以為這樣就能贏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太天真了  太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為我很擅長堆大雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只不過  最後一次堆還是在上小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,時限三十分鐘  不能使用工具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後  誰能堆出更好的雪人就算贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:08.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的雪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是大的雪人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼判斷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們相互打分評定唄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我還以為是比大小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼才是好的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦  也可以把大小算到分數裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她肯定是故意沒說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,藝術分和尺寸分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,靠綜合評分來定勝負啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:57.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  總之堆個大的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我就先去拿一下材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很從容啊  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,時間可只有三十分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:15.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣弄  儘量把中心弄得硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好  很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再做大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她怕了  她怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:36.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒想到我能堆這麼大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:40.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,身體做這麼大應該夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下面該做頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  看看高木同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很有雪人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,贏了的話要讓你幹什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再大  再大些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,必殺  滾雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還剩一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個大小怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然弄髒了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是這大小  肯定會比高木同學的雪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還剩三十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總之  先把雪人堆完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想想也是 滾起來都夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還剩15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總之  只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,畢竟西片的雪人都沒堆起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感覺就算完成了也贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用了  重得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且我都輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難得堆一次雪人  堆完它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完成了也贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感覺好像情侶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  這不是更像父母與孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:32.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,請我喝熱飲吧  無關勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哈？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.51,Takagi san—Picture 10-5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1466,400)}正月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好像看起來更霸氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個正月我在鑽研新的技藝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新的技藝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早餐吃30個年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:05.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吃得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,祝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,覺得好怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,賀年卡都寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還有必要這樣問好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這種儀式很重要的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看  不是有諺語這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一富士二鷹三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不四處問好會被五寸釘…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這可是新年  按儀式做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼正月會結束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我還想多過一會兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  你們正月都幹嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,放風箏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩和歌紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩雙六
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟親戚們玩的可開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你小學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗你都幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一直在跑步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是田徑部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在親戚家之間來回奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到處收壓歲錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:17.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,多虧他們  有錢買新鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,幹了很多事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在家裡躺著無所事事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  各有各的過法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:47.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能過來下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:50.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:56.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:58.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我有事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:08.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我問得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是濱口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:18.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,知道那傢伙有沒有什麼想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他馬上生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等等  你別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是他先送我禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是我要送他  只是回個禮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明白沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道他想要啥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你們倆關係不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我聽其他的女生說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北條最近似乎沉迷烤餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙不擅長做吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:09.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我有點想嚐嚐呢  北條親手做的曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他說想吃北條同學親手做的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼那傢伙會知道我迷上烤曲奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這  我不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙  想吃我的曲奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  也沒必要為他花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,濱口這種人  送他曲奇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再見  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這件事不要跟任何人提起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說起來  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,午休時你跟北條說話來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我路過看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你們都說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不要跟任何人提起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也沒說什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:21.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說的是秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比如濱口同學想要什麼東西  之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,隱約
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我猜對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一如既往地敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我又不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片有什麼想要的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:19.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我沒有跟北條討論這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟那個沒關係  只是我好奇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想作為選禮物的參考
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要送誰禮物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大概是15歲的男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比我大一歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不不  可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼能總是上她的套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肯定又在說狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那隻吉娃娃不是16歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是初三的男生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪  我還以為她又要來捉弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個…我不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再好好想一想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是關係到你自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是西片下個生日的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想好要什麼禮物了就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:36.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會有鬆了一口氣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒能把我跟北條說的事告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為我跟人家約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我好像使壞過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你不是一直在使壞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是一直捉弄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:33.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那…是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片送我的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.94,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:15.74,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:19.41,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:24.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.61,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君が住む山は「スノーランド」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:36.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一年中雪の降るこの国で    私は生まれたのと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.48,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君は話してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.40,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ねぇ    私は夏を見たことがないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:56.36,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}燃えるようなあの夏を    それを見るのが私の夢なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:58.85,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}でも良いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:06.92,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}この世界は知らない方がロマンチックな事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:13.16,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}たくさんあるのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.16,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.99,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:24.65,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.77,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の精？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:37.17,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の妖精とのファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.94,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}snow magic fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:15.74,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}被施加了雪之魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:19.41,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我對你一見傾心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:24.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}難道你就是雪之妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.61,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你住在名為「雪國」的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:36.25,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}降生於終年飄雪的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.48,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你曾對我如是訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.40,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}吶  我從未見過盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:56.36,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看那熾熱如火的盛夏  是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:58.85,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不過無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:06.92,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在這個世界上還有許多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:13.16,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因為未知才有的浪漫對吧
